Title: Weston: Target Eclipse
Descriptions: Well done on that last target. No longer will people be harrased by that dope. This next target is named Eclipse. As you can assume he's a shady S.O.B from the name. He had a lot of money before the fall, data say he build a cult and they prepared for the end of times. After the fall things got complacated with the Serpents and now they all work for them. Now this savage helps the Serpents keep order among their ranks. I need you to snipe this guy with one shot in the head to ensure he dies. He will be wating for his contact at a house south of Skalka. There is a spot on a cliff about 400m up the hill, it should be good enough.
